translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,11,Jo log yeh boht bara bohtan bandh laye hain yeh bhi tum mein say hi aik giroh hai. Tum issay apnay liye bura na samjho bulkay yeh to tumharay haq mein behtar hai. Haan inn mein say her aik shaks per itna gunah hai jitna uss ney kamaya hai aur inn mein say jiss ney iss kay boht baray hissay ko sir anjam diya hai uss kay liye azab bhi boht hi bara hai
  24,12,Issay suntay hi momin mard-o-aurton ney apnay haq mein nek gumani kiyon na ki aur kiyon na keh diya kay yeh to khullam khulla sareeh bohtan hai
  24,13,Woh iss per char gawah kiyon na laye? Aur jab gawah nahi laye to yeh bohtan baaz log yaqeenan Allah kay nazdeek mehaz jhootay hain
  24,14,Agar Allah Taalaa ka fazal-o-karam tum per duniya aur aakhirat mein na hota to yaqeenan tum ney jiss baat kay charchay shuroo ker rakhay thay iss baray mein tumhen boht bara azab phonchta
  24,15,Jabkay tum issay apni zabano say naqal dar naqal kerney lagay aur apnay mun say woh baat nikalney lagay jiss ki tumhen mutlaq khabar na thi go tum issay halki baat samajhtay rahey lekin Allah Taalaa kay nazdeek woh boht bari baat thi
  24,16,Tum ney aisi baat ko suntay hi kiyon na keh diya kay humen aisi baat mun say nikalni bhi laeeq nahi. Ya-Allah! Tu pak hai yeh to boht bara bohtan hai aur tohmat hai
  24,17,Allah Taalaa tumhen naseehat kerta hai kay phir kabhi bhi aisa kaam na kerna agar tum sachay momin ho
  24,18,Allah Taalaa tumharay samney apni aayaten biyan farma raha hai aur Allah Taalaa ilm-o-hikmat wala hai
  24,19,Jo log musalmano mein bay hayaee phelaney kay aarzoo mand rehtay hain unn kay liye duniya aur aakhirat mein dard-naak azab hain Allah sab kuch janta hai aur tum kuch bhi nahi jantay
  24,20,Agar tum per Allah Taalaa ka fazal aur uss ki rehmat na hoti aur yeh bhi kay Allah Taalaa bari shafqat rakhney wala meharban hai. (to tum per azab utar jata)